{"id":311420,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/08/维权网-福州冤民陈气被迫害坐牢，全家老少举牌/","date":"2013-08-31T01:04:24Z","modified":"2013-08-31T01:04:24Z","title":"维权网 | 福州冤民陈气被迫害坐牢，全家老少举牌齐声讨（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div><span></span></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a><span><br /></span></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员林仙报道）日前，已古稀之年的福州女冤民陈气妈妈和一对未成年的儿女，在强拆成残垣断壁废墟的家园前举牌抗议，全家老少齐声讨鼓楼公安分局公然制造冤案！</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>女冤民陈气因参与抬棺维权，誓死保卫家园抗暴力强拆，惨遭福州鼓楼分局以“寻衅滋事”刑拘。当时自发和陈气一起抬棺维权的冤民有近</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">70</span><span>人，鼓楼分局在事发两天后才有选择地只将陈气一人抓捕。鼓楼分局既然认定抬棺维权的冤民触犯刑法，为何不追诉其他“同案犯”，而是选择性执法！</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>维权本无罪，显然，鼓楼分局抓捕陈气，是在报复迫害！冤民陈气已离婚多年，是家里名副其实的顶梁柱。现陈气旧冤未雪，又添新冤，一人坐牢，年迈的老母亲和一对未成年的儿子无人照管。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>老母亲举牌要求无罪释放女儿，未成年一对儿女要妈妈回家，令人潸然泪下！</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-30-5ixSTBTw/UiCp3n_0XjI/AAAAAAAAngw/sAaviN3mhpc/s1600/QQ%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%87.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-30-5ixSTBTw/UiCp3n_0XjI/AAAAAAAAngw/sAaviN3mhpc/s320/QQ%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%87.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-ZUhiBjEVFvQ/UiCp5rLCEPI/AAAAAAAAng4/94lEjI5E62g/s1600/QQ%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%8720130829212952.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-ZUhiBjEVFvQ/UiCp5rLCEPI/AAAAAAAAng4/94lEjI5E62g/s320/QQ%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%8720130829212952.jpg\" width=\"240\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-lnp_JPUAiOQ/UiCp99hOA3I/AAAAAAAAnhA/YvuaWtYJenA/s1600/QQ%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%8720130829212958.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-lnp_JPUAiOQ/UiCp99hOA3I/AAAAAAAAnhA/YvuaWtYJenA/s320/QQ%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%8720